    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8078-afde-ec1d59127121",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Dropout is important to control for, so authors analyze the different reasons that may justify dropout from a higher education institution. The main reason authors found were interest and performance in an undergraduate program. Authors look at dropout using hierarchical clustering and identify multiple motives behind it.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8078-afde-ec1d59127121",
